name: rebuild
description:
The world feels more divided than I’ve ever experienced in my waking life. A pandemic that is taking/destroying lives and completely shaking up the global stage.

I hope that out of this crazy ride, we learn that it’s us who are at the mercy when things get tough and we put aside our differences and look to do our parts whether big or small - to build a better foundation for our future.
